 - Click OK

Alternatively, run the following PowerCLI command:

# Set Syslog.global.logDir for each host
Get-VMHost | Foreach { Set-AdvancedConfiguration -VMHost $_ -Name Syslog.global.logDir -Value \"<NewLocation>\" }"
